        "content": [
            "王子追上了绯龙。\\n龙化后的王子想帮助绯龙阻止火山喷发。\\n但绯龙不愿领地被他人插足，极力反对。\\n为了平息即将喷发的火山，\\n王子只能战胜绯龙，与其缔结契约。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n阿德拉火山\\n火山口\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "呃……\\n紊乱的魔力……无法平息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "听我的话啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "至少要坚持到那群人逃出去为止，\\n不能让它喷发！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里就是火山口吗！绯龙，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "咦……等、等等！\\n你们怎么跑到这里来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "绯龙，我们来帮你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不能让受伤的你\\n独自承受这一切！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "不用你们帮忙！\\n我不打算借助任何人的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你浑身是伤，\\n就别逞强了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "现在的你，能做什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "真没礼貌啊，你这森隐族的家伙！\\n你以为我是谁啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我会龙化，\\n应该多少能帮上点忙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "等、等一下！你在干吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "如果非要做到那种地步，\\n还不如和你缔结契约！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "我不想让别的龙\\n染指这块土地！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "如果缔结契约，把魔力转化为契约石，\\n说不定能抑制失控！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好的……\\n绯龙！和我缔结契约吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "“嗯，我很乐意！”\\n要是就这么轻易地答应你，\\n岂不是显得我很没节操。\\n感觉像个轻浮的女人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "省略神圣的仪式\\n这可不太好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "规矩就是规矩。\\n想要缔结契约，就让我见识下你的力量吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_INGAMESTORY_03_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
